href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/29/24208656/apple-intelligence-ai-ios-18-1-iphone-16-launch&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/29/24208656/apple-intelligence-ai-ios-18-1-iphone-16-launch" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/29/24208656/apple-intelligence-ai-ios-18-1-iphone-16-launch</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-29T10:27:43-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-29T10:27:43-04:00</updated><title> Arc&#39;teryx 的新款动力裤可以让徒步旅行者感觉轻了 30 磅</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一位徒步旅行者穿着 Arc&#39;teryx 的新型动力 MO/GO 裤子进行高空骑行。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/IqcQoW0Ix1043MKgBy4i-Q7D_ic=/0x0:2400x1600/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73488410/arcteryx.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Arc&#39;teryx 的新型动力 MO/GO 裤子声称可将腿部力量提高高达 40%。&lt;/em>; |图片：Arc&#39;teryx&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;egkyk0&quot;>;增强力量的外骨骼套装可以帮助&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2017/12/5/ 16726004/verge-next-level-season-two-induscial-exo骨骼-ford-ekso-suitx&quot;>;体力劳动的工作&lt;/a>;感觉&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2017/5 /15/15640176/exosculpt-warehouse-lifting-lowes-virginia-tech&quot;>;不太费力&lt;/a>;，但 Arc&#39;teryx 与 Google X Labs 的子公司 Skip 合作，将该技术带入休闲时光。这款动力&lt;a href=&quot;https://squamish.arcteryxacademy.com/mo/go&quot;>;MO/GO 裤子&lt;/a>;在膝盖处配备了轻型电动马达，可以增强徒步旅行者上坡时的腿部力量，同时还能增强徒步旅行者的腿部力量。吸收下降过程中脚步的冲击力。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;hXsTQb&quot;>;MO/GO（山羊的缩写）裤子重约 7 磅，配有增强模块和三小时充电电池随附的。该模块通过每条腿的一对碳纤维支架固定在徒步旅行者身上，支架隐藏在 Arc&#39;teryx Gamma 徒步裤下方，使设备易于穿脱。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;qRgOb9&quot;>; &lt;div style=&quot;left: 0; width: 100%; height: 0;position:relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%;&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;8dBq3x&quot;>;作为...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/29/24208615/arcteryx-skip-google-x-labs-mogo-hiking-exo骨骼&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/29/24208615/arcteryx-skip-google-x-labs-mogo-hiking-exoskeleton" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/29/24208615/arcteryx-skip-google-x-labs-mogo-hiking-exo骨骼</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-29T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-29T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title>罗技首席执行官 Hanneke Faber 希望您的下一款鼠标能够永远耐用</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;罗技首席执行官 Hanneke Faber 的肖像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/mtozaHdI2U7qjfBCGoVi361O4qw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73488331/DCD_Hanneke_Faber.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 The Verge 提供/照片由 Logitech 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;罗技的新任主管讨论了公司恢复增长的问题，并计划将其碳足迹减少一半。&lt;/p>; &lt;p >; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24206847/logitech-ceo-hanneke-faber-mouse-keyboard-gaming-decoder-podcast-interview&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24206847/logitech-ceo-hanneke-faber-mouse-keyboard-gaming-decoder-podcast-interview" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24206847/logitech-ceo-hanneke-faber-mouse-keyboard-gaming-decoder-podcast-interview</id><author><name>尼莱·帕特尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-29T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-29T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title> AI 记录分数</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-bTbGwWJTJe0uwIoFtY3gnSPgpc=/2x0:2177x1450/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/ 73488228/lede_gymnastics.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;lGL1DY&quot;>;当西蒙·拜尔斯 (Simone Biles) 在比利时安特卫普体育馆向评委致敬并走上垫子跳马时，似乎场内的每一个摄像机拥挤的竞技场正在对她进行训练。观众们纷纷掏出智能手机进行录制。摄影师们从他们的媒体位置进行放大。当她冲上跳板时，一台电视摄像机跟踪她乘坐高速移动车沿着跑道一路奔跑。上方摆动的蜘蛛摄像头捕捉到了她身体向上的轨迹，她转向桌子，向上一挡，扭动一圈半，落在蓝色垫子上，双臂举过头顶。人类运动能力和动觉之美的巅峰已经被捕捉到。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;SpRGqe&quot;>;但还有其他......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/c/24182327/olympics-gymnastics-ai-judging-fujitsu-jss-fig&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/c/24182327/olympics-gymnastics-ai-judging-fujitsu-jss-fig" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/c/24182327/olympics-gymnastics-ai-judging-fujitsu-jss-fig</id><author><name>德沃拉·迈耶斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-29T05:27:38-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-29T05:27:38-04:00</updated><title>谷歌的新 Nest Learning Thermostat 具有改进的用户界面和“无边框”显示屏</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google 第四代 Nest Learning Thermostat&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/p0dLWuNb_dAfJSgUB02wWqbP_IY=/319x0:3777x2305/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/73487910/nest4thgenthermostatleak.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：MysteryLupin (&lt;a class=&quot;ql-link&quot; href=&quot;https://x.com/MysteryLupin/status/1817682764595970361&quot; 目标=&quot;_blank&quot;>;X&lt;/a>;)&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;rYJKPy&quot;>;Google 似乎正准备推出第四代 Nest Learning Thermostat。有关恒温器的详细信息&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/24/24205541/google-nest-learning-thermostat-4th-gen-leaks&quot;>;上周首次泄露&lt;/a>; ，现在同一个泄密者在 X 上发布了更多 &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/MysteryLupin/status/1817682764595970361&quot;>;文档&lt;/a>;，显示这个新模型将有一个可定制的主屏幕，一个新的“动态远视”功能和“无边框”显示屏。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;3RY4V1&quot;>;泄漏详细介绍了“高分辨率无边框显示屏”，看起来它将允许 Nest Learning Thermostat 的 UI延伸到现有第三代设备上通常为黑色边框的区域。其他泄露的图像显示 UI 元素也更接近显示屏的边框。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图像：MysteryLupin (&lt;a class=&quot;ql-link&quot; href =&quot;https://x.com/MysteryLupin/status/1817682779762508112&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;X&lt;/a>;)&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;第四代 Nest Learning Thermostat 的泄露规格。 &lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;nA4NU5&quot;>;D...&lt;/p>; &l